# Cline Rules — Find My Expert

## Project Context

**Find My Expert** is an internal SAP expert directory for SAP Austria.

- **CAP Backend**: `@sap/cds ^9.x`, Node.js 22, SQLite (local) / PostgreSQL (prod)
- **SAPUI5 Frontend**: Fiori Elements (List Report + Object Page), OData V4, `sap_horizon` Theme
- **Service**: `CatalogService` at `/api/catalog` (requires `ExpertViewer` or `Admin` role)
- **Deployment Target**: SAP BTP Work Zone
- **Project Root**: `/workspaces/find-my-expert`

### Start Commands

```bash
# Full-stack with FLP sandbox (recommended)
npm run watch-flp     # → http://localhost:4004/findmyexpert-search/webapp/test/flpSandbox.html#Shell-home

# Full-stack with individual app
npm run watch-search          # → findmyexpert-search
npm run watch-manage-experts  # → findmyexpert-manage-experts
npm run watch-manage-roles    # → findmyexpert-manage-roles
npm run watch-manage-topics   # → findmyexpert-manage-topics

# CAP backend only
npm run watch                 # → http://localhost:4004
```

---

## App Inventory

| App | Path | Service | Base Entity | Watch Script |
