| Manage Experts | `app/findmyexpert-manage-experts` | `CatalogService` | `Experts` | `npm run watch-manage-experts` |
| Manage Roles | `app/findmyexpert-manage-roles` | `CatalogService` | `ExpertRoles` | `npm run watch-manage-roles` |
